  <li>
    <p>From the south came silent coveys of starlings and thrushes, flying very high, but always <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="giving the town a wide berth - (berth - sufficient distance for maneuvering a ship)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(对小镇敬而远之)</code></b>, as though the strange implement of the plague described by Paneloux, the giant flail whirling and shrilling over the house tops, warned them off us.</p>
  </li>
