    <p>When told of some <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="unlooked-for"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(意想不到的)</code></b> recovery, they <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="made a show of interest"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(装作感兴趣的样子)</code></b>, but actually received the news with the stolid indifference.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>One could see that the strain was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="telling on"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(在...身上产生效果/发生影响[负面影响])</code></b> him, and if he managed to keep going, it was thanks to two or three fixed ideas.</p>
