  <li>
    <p>He had kept the news to himself so far and could only <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="put it down to"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(把...归因于)</code></b> his nervous exhaustion that he <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="passed it on to Grand - (pass on - 告知/传递信息)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(向 Grand 谈起这件事来)</code></b>.</p>
